---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Hello Genie is on a mission to democratize AI for small businesses — smart automation that's simple, affordable, and built for real business owners.">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-16">

    <!-- ════ HERO ════ -->
    <section class="hero-bg section-padding wave-divider relative" style="padding-top: 7rem; padding-bottom: 6rem;">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
        <div class="badge-pill bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 mx-auto w-fit mb-6 animate-fade-in">About Us</div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-gray-900 leading-[1.1] tracking-tight animate-fade-in animate-delay-1">
          AI That Works<br /><span class="gradient-text">For You</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed animate-fade-in animate-delay-2">
          We believe every small business deserves the same AI-powered efficiency that Fortune 500 companies take for granted. Hello Genie makes that possible — no technical expertise required.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ════ MISSION ════ -->
    <section class="section-light section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto reveal">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <div class="badge-pill bg-orange-100 text-orange-700 w-fit mb-4">Our Mission</div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-tight">Democratize AI for<br />Small Business</h2>
            <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Small businesses are the backbone of the economy, but they're drowning in admin work. Scheduling, emails, invoices, data entry — it never ends. Enterprise companies have armies of staff and expensive software. You shouldn't need either.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Hello Genie is the AI assistant every business owner wishes they had — one that handles the repetitive work so you can focus on serving customers and growing your vision.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="feature-card p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🎯</div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-black gradient-text">40%</div>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Time saved on admin</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl mb-2">⚡</div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-black gradient-text">5 min</div>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Setup time</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🔒</div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-black gradient-text">100%</div>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Data privacy</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl mb-2">💬</div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-black gradient-text">24/7</div>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">AI availability</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ════ WHY WE BUILT THIS ════ -->
    <section class="section-warm section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto reveal">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <div class="badge-pill bg-pink-100 text-pink-700 mx-auto w-fit mb-4">Our Story</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">Why We Built Hello Genie</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card p-10 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            We watched brilliant entrepreneurs — bakery owners, fitness coaches, freelance designers, local consultants — spend their evenings doing data entry instead of perfecting their craft. They didn't need complex enterprise software. They needed a simple, smart assistant that just works.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            That's why we built Hello Genie. Not another SaaS dashboard. Not another tool to learn. An AI assistant that plugs into your existing tools and handles the work you shouldn't be doing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ════ VALUES ════ -->
    <section class="section-light section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto reveal">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <div class="badge-pill bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 mx-auto w-fit mb-4">Our Values</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900">What We Believe</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="feature-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🪄</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Simple is Better</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">If it takes more than 5 minutes to set up, we failed. Technology should simplify your life, not add another learning curve.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🤝</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Your Data, Your Rules</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We never sell your data. We never train on your data. Your business information stays exactly where it should — with you.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">💡</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">AI With Heart</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">We build AI that feels human. Your customers should never know they're talking to an AI unless you want them to.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ════ CTA ════ -->
    <section class="section-purple section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center reveal">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">
          Join the Movement
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-purple-200 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">Be part of the community of business owners taking their time back with AI.</p>
        <div class="mt-10">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-white text-base">Join the Waitlist</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
